data.description: MLS #269979 Welcome to 8719 W Entiat AVE. located in the heart of Kennewick. With nearly 2,100 sq ft this home has everything you have been looking for. Sitting on a corner lot, you get lots of room for parking. Entering you will find a tile entryway that will lead you up to the main living space all with new hardwood floors and a beautiful tile fireplace that will keep you cozy in those cold winter nights. Enjoy dinner in your formal dining area filled with lots of natural lighting. Enjoy the spacious kitchen with waterproof hardwood floors and a window that looks out to your backyard. Just a couple of steps down you will find the lower-level living space with a pellet stove, half a bathroom and one bedroom. In the upper level you will find the other 3 bedrooms, one being the primary suite and the guest bath. The backyard is fully fenced and has mature fruit trees. Conveniently located just minutes from shopping and dining. Don’t wait, call today to schedule your personal tour.
